### Travel Planner API Tests

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### Health Check
GET {{apiUrl}}/health

### Register User
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "full_name": "Test User",
    "password": "testpassword123"
}

### Login User
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "testpassword123"
}

### Get Current User (requires token)
GET {{apiUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Search Destinations
GET {{apiUrl}}/destinations/search?query=paris&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Weather
GET {{apiUrl}}/weather/current?city=paris
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Plan Trip
POST {{apiUrl}}/trips/plan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "destination": "Paris",
    "start_date": "2024-06-01",
    "end_date": "2024-06-07",
    "budget": 2000,
    "travelers_count": 2,
    "trip_type": "Couple",
    "accommodation_preference": "Hotel",
    "interests": ["culture", "food", "shopping"],
    "pace": "Balanced"
}

### Search Flights
POST {{apiUrl}}/bookings/flights/search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "origin": "NYC",
    "destination": "CDG",
    "departure_date": "2024-06-01",
    "passengers": 2,
    "travel_class": "Economy"
}

### Search Hotels
POST {{apiUrl}}/bookings/hotels/search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "city": "Paris",
    "check_in_date": "2024-06-01",
    "check_out_date": "2024-06-07",
    "guests": 2,
    "rooms": 1,
    "star_rating": 4
}

### Search Trains
POST {{apiUrl}}/bookings/trains/search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "origin_station": "New Delhi",
    "destination_station": "Mumbai",
    "departure_date": "2024-06-01",
    "passengers": 2,
    "train_class": "3A"
}